title: Peta-Gay Booth
text:
I am new to NCH and the business world. So far I have worked with Hunter, Erika and Christine. They have been great! This is my first experience setting up a business and it is a BEAST! Each team member I have encountered so far has been very knowledgeable, patient,and a great teacher and communicator. I am never rushed or pressured or left confused. I look forward to meeting the rest of my powerhouse team of experts at NCH. Incorporating properly is an overwhelming process but you don't have to be overwhelmed or fearful of error with NCH at your back!!
Peta-Gay
IDEAL Home & Property Solutions
